IF EXISTS
    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CategoriesId], [d0].[Code], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Description], [d0].[KKal], [d0].[Name], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[Price], [d0].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d0]
    WHERE ([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t] ON [d].[DishId] = [t].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[ComplexId], [u].[IsComplex], [u].[Price], [u].[Quantity]
    FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
    WHERE (([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t0] ON [d].[DishId] = [t0].[DishId]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [d1].[DishId], [d1].[IngredientId], [d1].[CompanyId], [d1].[Proportion]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d1]
    WHERE ([d1].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [d].[DishId] = [t1].[DishId]
INNER JOIN (

    FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
    WHERE ([i].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t2] ON [t1].[IngredientId] = [t2].[Id]
WHERE (([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)

IF EXISTS
    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

SELECT [t1].[Id] AS [IngredientId], [t1].[Name] AS [IngredientName], SUM(CAST([u].[Quantity] AS decimal(18,2)) * [t0].[Proportion]) AS [Quantity], [t1].[MeasureUnit], SUM([u].[Quantity]) AS [DishQuantity]
FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[CategoriesId], [d].[Code], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Description], [d].[KKal], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], [d].[Price], [d].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t] ON [u].[DishId] = [t].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d0]
    WHERE ([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
    FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
    WHERE ([i].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [t0].[IngredientId] = [t1].[Id]
WHERE (([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
GROUP BY [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[MeasureUnit]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Number], [t1].[Date], [t].[LineId], [t].[IngredientsId], [t].[Quantity], [t].[ValidUntil], [i0].[Id], [t].[CompanyId], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[Id] AS [Id1]
    FROM [Ingredients] AS [i0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [c].[CompanyId], [c].[LineId], [c].[IngredientsId], [c].[InitialQuantity], [c].[Price], [c].[Quantity], [c].[ValidUntil]
        FROM [Consignment] AS [c]
        WHERE ([c].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [i0].[Id] = [t].[IngredientsId]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[DocsId], [d].[IngredientsId], [d].[Number], [d].[Price], [d].[Quantity]
        FROM [DocLines] AS [d]
        WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
    ) AS [t0] ON [t].[LineId] = [t0].[Id]

        WHERE ([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
    ) AS [t1] ON [t0].[DocsId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE ([i0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t2] ON [i].[Id] = [t2].[IngredientsId]
WHERE ([i].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL

FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Number], [t1].[Date], [t].[LineId], [t].[IngredientsId], [t].[Quantity], [t].[ValidUntil], [i0].[Id], [t].[CompanyId], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[Id] AS [Id1]
    FROM [Ingredients] AS [i0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [c].[CompanyId], [c].[LineId], [c].[IngredientsId], [c].[InitialQuantity], [c].[Price], [c].[Quantity], [c].[ValidUntil]
        FROM [Consignment] AS [c]
        WHERE ([c].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [i0].[Id] = [t].[IngredientsId]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[DocsId], [d].[IngredientsId], [d].[Number], [d].[Price], [d].[Quantity]
        FROM [DocLines] AS [d]
        WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
    ) AS [t0] ON [t].[LineId] = [t0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Date], [d0].[Description], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Type]
        FROM [Docs] AS [d0]
        WHERE ([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
    ) AS [t1] ON [t0].[DocsId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE ([i0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t2] ON [i].[Id] = [t2].[IngredientsId]
WHERE ([i].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL

        SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Date], [d0].[Description], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Type]
        FROM [Docs] AS [d0]
        WHERE ([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
    ) AS [t1] ON [t0].[DocsId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE ([i0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t2] ON [i].[Id] = [t2].[IngredientsId]
WHERE ([i].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY [i].[Id], [t2].[Id], [t2].[CompanyId], [t2].[LineId], [t2].[IngredientsId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id1]

     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0

         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]

)

     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0

     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'

         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]

)
